sentences: Issa Bagayogo (1961 – 10 October 2016) was a Malian musician.
Bagayogo died after a long illness on 10 October 2016.
Sya, originally released in 1998, was the first album released under Six Degrees Records.
In 2004, Bagayogo released his album called Tassoumakan, which means "voice of fire", followed by Mali Koura in 2008.
